latestPosts.caption:
#67 @forbesindia Top 100 Digital Stars 2024😭❤️‍🔥

Look Mumma and Pappaaaa your little girl has made it to Forbes. 
5 years of consistency and hard work feels so worth it today🥺♥️

I’m sooo emotional and happy today. Started in 2019 to represent brown girlies. To be recognized from South India and represent my state on a larger scale. To empower women and bring a small change. This was all just a teenage dream. 

This could not be ever possible without you guys! 2023 has been the hardest on me mentally and physically. I kept going because of my online family. The huge support and love that you guys show me every single day. THANKYOU MY BABIES♥️

Thankyou for everything you’ve given me. Thankyou @forbesindia for recognizing the work we’ve put in. I owe it to you guys, to my team @honeycombtalent and to my loved ones. 

I’M SOOOOO HAPPYYYYYYY🥹❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥
If I could do this, You could do this too. NEVER STOP DREAMING✨

Temple theme Pelli look🧿♥️✨

This look is so close to my heart because it’s ancient temple theme. I put so much thought into each jewellery and fabric that went into this one. I felt so powerful with all the goddesses on me. 
I’m a huge devotee of Shakthi and I wanted to represent it through my art and what I do the best🥹🧿

I wanted tanjavur painting on my blouse and @sowmyareddysr understood my vision and got it done just like how I wanted which turned out incredibly beautiful. She also added tassles to make this even more unique and royal. 

I’m also glad I book Afsha to see if I want ger to do my makeup on my wedding day. I personally loved the look. Very different from how I do my makeup. Although my marriage got postponed, I know who is going to do my makeup on my big day. She was honestly expensive but I personally think she’s worth every penny I paid for this makeup.
